---
import { studioName } from "@zoggy/branding";
import StudioLayout from "../../layouts/StudioLayout.astro";

const title = `Development Supervisor | ${studioName}`;
const description = `A Go-based internal development tool for building, launching, monitoring, and troubleshooting the MMO server.`;
---

<StudioLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <section class="sup-hero" aria-labelledby="sup-title">
    <div class="sup-hero-inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">Internal tool</p>
      <h1 id="sup-title">Development Supervisor</h1>
      <p class="sup-lead">A Go-based control suite for building, launching, monitoring, and troubleshooting the game server and its supporting services.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" aria-label="Problem">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-heading" style="max-width: 100%; text-align: center">
        <h2>Born from a practical problem</h2>
        <p style="max-width: 48rem; margin: 0 auto">Launching several development services without enough visibility into build failures, startup ordering, connection problems, or hanging processes. The Control Suite became the answer.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" aria-label="Architecture">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="arch-callout">
        <div class="arch-flow">
          <span class="arch-node">Control Suite</span>
          <span class="arch-arrow" aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
          <span class="arch-node">Supervisor</span>
          <span class="arch-arrow" aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
          <span class="arch-node">Game Server</span>
        </div>
        <p>A three-layer architecture: the dashboard frontend communicates with a supervisor process that manages game server instances, monitors their health, and reports status changes.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" aria-label="Features">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <h2>Key features</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="wide-grid">
        <article class="card feature-card">
          <span class="feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#9776;</span>
          <h3>Live console output</h3>
          <p>Real-time server process output streamed to the dashboard.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card feature-card">
          <span class="feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#9673;</span>
          <h3>Build tracking</h3>
          <p>Build and launch stage visibility from source to running service.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card feature-card">
          <span class="feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#9733;</span>
          <h3>Health monitoring</h3>
          <p>Process health states, restart behavior, and crash recovery.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card feature-card">
          <span class="feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#9881;</span>
          <h3>Connection status</h3>
          <p>Server connection monitoring with error and warning panels.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" aria-label="Why it matters">
    <div class="section-inner wide-grid">
      <article class="card text-stack">
        <h2>Why it matters</h2>
        <p>This project demonstrates that Zoggy Studios is not merely brainstorming a game. The studio creates supporting technology around its projects: practical tools that solve real engineering problems.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card text-stack">
        <h2>Built with</h2>
        <p>Go, process management, WebSocket streaming, structured logging. Designed for the development environment with potential server-administration applications later.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</StudioLayout>

<style>
  .sup-hero {
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 12% 18%, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.3), transparent 22rem),
      radial-gradient(circle at 88% 22%, rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.2), transparent 20rem),
      linear-gradient(160deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 52%, #020617 100%);
    color: #f8fafc;
    min-height: min(520px, 60svh);
    display: grid;
    align-items: center;
    padding: clamp(3rem, 9vw, 6rem) var(--space-page);
  }

  .sup-hero-inner {
    width: min(100%, 72rem);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .sup-hero .eyebrow {
    color: #34d399;
  }

  .sup-hero h1 {
    color: #f8fafc;
    text-shadow: 0 0 2rem rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.25);
  }

  .sup-lead {
    max-width: 46rem;
    margin: clamp(1.25rem, 3vw, 2rem) 0 0;
    font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 2.5vw, 1.6rem);
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: #cbd5e1;
  }

  .arch-callout {
    border-radius: var(--radius-card);
    padding: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    border: 1px solid rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.12);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.62);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .arch-flow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .arch-node {
    display: inline-flex;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    background: #111827;
    color: #38bdf8;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .arch-arrow {
    color: #64748b;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
  }

  .feature-card {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    color: #374151;
  }

  .feature-icon {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 2.5rem;
    height: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    background: #111827;
    color: #38bdf8;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
</style>
